'''同纹螺科'''（學名：{{lang|la|Amastridae}}），又名'''岛居蜗牛科'''<ref name="zhihu">{{zhihu |type=question |id=30634616 |title=世界上有哪些很稀有的动物？ |date=2019-01-04 |access-date=2020-07-27}}</ref> ，按[[生物分类学|生物分类学]]屬於體型細小、會呼吸空氣的{{tsl|en|land snail|陸生蝸牛}}的[[科_(生物)|科]]，是一種[[陆生动物|陸生]][[肺螺類|肺螺類]][[腹足纲|腹足纲]][[软体动物|软体动物]]{{r|WoRMS_994718}}。舊屬[[槲果螺總科|槲果螺總科]]的成員<ref name="Bouchet 2005">{{Bouchet 2005}}</ref>，今隨同槲果螺總科被合併進[[蛹螺下目|蛹螺下目]]的[[蛹螺总科|蛹螺总科]]<ref name="Bouchet 2017">{{Bouchet 2017}}</ref>。

本科有物種近300種，皆為[[夏威夷群島|夏威夷群島]]的[[特有種|特有種]]，但當中可能有超過九成均已{{tsl|en|List of extinct animals of the Hawaiian Islands#Mollusks|夏威夷已滅絕動物列表|滅絕}}{{r|zhihu}}<ref name="Amastridae">{{cite journal |first1=Charles |last1=Lydeard |first2=Robert H. |last2=Cowie |first3=Winston F. |last3=Ponder |authorlink3=溫斯頓·旁德 |first4=Arthur E. |last4=Bogan |first5=Philippe |last5=Bouchet |authorlink5=菲利普·布歇特 |first6=Stephanie A. |last6=Clark |first7=Kevin S. |last7=Cummings |first8=Terrence J. |last8=Frest |first9=Olivier |last9=Gargominy |first10=Dai G. |last10=Herbert |first11=Robert |last11=Hershler |first12=Kathryn E. |last12=Perez |first13=Barry |last13=Roth |first14=Mary |last14=Seddon |first15=Ellen E. |last15=Strong |first16=Fred G. |last16=Thompson |title=The Global Decline of Nonmarine Mollusks |journal=''[[BioScience|BioScience]]'' |volume=54 |issue=4 |pages=321-330 |year=2004 |date=2004-04 |url=http://www.unc.edu/~keperez/lydeard_bioscience.pdf |format=PDF |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606083531/http://www.unc.edu/~keperez/lydeard_bioscience.pdf |archive-date=2013-06-06 |access-date=2020-07-27 |language=en }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Alan |last=Solem |title=''How many Hawaiian Land Snail species are left? and What We Can Do for Them.'' |journal=Bishop Museum Occasional Papers |issue=30 |pages=27-40 |location=[[檀香山|Honolulu]]（[[美國|美國]][[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]） |year=1990 |url=http://hbs.bishopmuseum.org/pubs-online/pdf/op30p27.pdf |format=PDF |language=en |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711095506/http://hbs.bishopmuseum.org/pubs-online/pdf/op30p27.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://thomvandooren.org/2013/02/28/last_snail/ |last=van Dooren |first=Thom |title=The last snail: conservation and extinction in Hawai-{’}-i |date=2013-02-28 |access-date=2020-07-27 |language=en }}</ref>。牠們的體長均不超過50毫米<ref name="Schileyko 1998">{{cite journal |first=Anatolij A. |last=Schileyko |year=1998 |title